title: The Medieval Islamic Civilization - C. 10 (Art, Architecture 3)
description:
The Medieval Islamic Civilization - Collection 10 (Art, Architecture 3):

We have 8 titles here:

-  Greenhalgh - Constantinople to Cordoba; Dismantling Ancient Architecture in the East, North Africa and Islamic Spain (2012)

-  Hakim - Arabic-Islamic Cities; Building and Planning Principles (2010)

-  Bloom - The Minbar from the Kutubiyya Mosque (1998)

-  Behrens-Abouseif - Islamic Architecture in Cairo; an Introduction (1998)

-  George - Picturing Islam; Art and Ethics in a Muslim Lifeworld (2010)

-  Schimmel - Calligraphy and Islamic Culture (1984)

-  Rice - Islamic Art (1965)

-  Ettinghausen et al - The Art and Architecture of Islam, 650-1250 (2001)
